<p><strong>Skills</strong> Nature +4, Perception +5, Stealth +6, Survival +5</p>

<p><strong>Languages</strong> any one language (usually Common)</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1/2 (100 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Hearing and Sight.</em></strong> The scout has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on hearing or sight.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The scout makes two melee attacks or two ranged attacks.</p>

<p><strong><em>Shortsword.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Longbow.</em></strong> Ranged Weapon Attack: +4 to hit, ranged 150/600 ft., one target. Hit: 6 (1d8 + 2) piercing damage.</p>

